data.description:
Experience the blend of comfort and potential with this modern multi-family home in Flatbush, now featuring a fully detached two car port for added convenience. Designed with dual living spaces, this property is a prime choice for both families and individuals looking to maximize their financial opportunities. Live in one unit while generating income from the other, allowing the rental earnings to contribute meaningfully to your urban lifestyle.
The location of this property is of utmost importance, providing easy access to all the conveniences Brooklyn and the surrounding areas have to offer. Positioned just a short distance from vital subway lines and bus stops, navigating through Brooklyn and beyond becomes incredibly straightforward. Whether youre headed to an important meeting, an exciting show, or a night out, Manhattan is readily accessible, placing you just minutes away from its lively center. This proximity to the citys dynamism, along with the distinct benefits of residing in Brooklyn, affords you a lifestyle that truly offers the best of both worlds.
Flatbush itself is bustling with activity, marked by vibrant streets and a lively community. When youre in need of a pause from the urban excitement, numerous parks and green spaces are nearby, offering peaceful havens of tranquility. Investing in this home means investing in a lifestyle of convenience, adaptability, and boundless potential. The addition of a two car port only amplifies the propertys appeal, ensuring that your parking needs are seamlessly met, and adding an extra layer of practicality to your investment.
